title: CAFA Championship
text:
The CAFA Championship is an international <a href="Association%20football">football</a> competition in <a href="Central%20Asia">Central Asia</a> for the member nations of the <a href="Central%20Asian%20Football%20Association">Central Asian Football Association</a> (CAFA).
History.
The inaugural edition of the tournament was planned to be hosted by <a href="Tashkent">Tashkent</a> in October 2018. It was not played out though.
Results.
Senior tournaments.
Men's.
No edition took place yet or is planned currently.
U-23 tournaments.
Men's.
No men's under 23 tournament has been planned yet.
